<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good morning Rafa=
ella,</span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">As per the next p=
hase of the process map =E2=80=93 Stephen Walker from ASURNZ =E2=80=93 our =
Technical Building Consultant is due to visit site and author the scope of =
works required.</span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Stephen and I wil=
l be visiting site at<span class=3D"x_apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><=
u>12:30 today</u><span class=3D"x_apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>to co=
mplete the walk-through and determine the scope-of-works
 for the repairs to your home.</span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Once we have comp=
leted this document =E2=80=93 I can return and go through each item on the =
scope line-by-line in detail with you so you can gain the confidence that w=
e have captured everything.</span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">When we go throug=
h the scope together =E2=80=93 we can consider adding anything further that=
 is necessary if we need to. I am exceptionally confident that Stephen and =
I will capture everything on the first draft
 =E2=80=93 but I want you to know that you will sign-off on the scope-of-wo=
rks as being complete before we move to the repair phase.</span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You do not need t=
o join us for today=E2=80=99s visit =E2=80=93 but you are more than welcome=
 to if you wish. As I stated =E2=80=93 we can review it together once compl=
ete. I will let you decide whether you wish to join us or not.</span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please do not hes=
itate to contact me if you have any questions or concerns at all.</span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Many Thanks,</spa=
n></p>
